<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Boil water, honey, sugar until dissolved, then cool]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Blend fruit, alcohol with syrup, then freeze in air tight container]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Whisk together eggs, sugar]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Melt together olive oil, butter, then add to the egg and sugar]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Grind the hazelnuts in a food processor until fine then add to the mixture]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add baking powder, flour, polenta to the mixture]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add vanilla pods to the mixture]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Put mixture in oiled 23 cm and bake 175Â° for 25 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Let cool in the tin, then dust with icing sugar and serve with sorbet]]></step>
